The Lionsgate Troll of 2006 occurred in early December 2006, when [[Troll|Hrodulf]], a [[New York|turd-sucking douchebag with no decency]], [[butthurt]] concerning the [http://forums.lionsgate.com/forumdisplay.php?f=108 Lionsgate Saw III forum] censoring the word "racism," and the stupidity of the ignorant sawfags that infested the forum, decided to try to own the forum, film company, and sawfags in one fell swoop.  Unbeknownst to him, his silly attempt at trolling was soon forgotten and he didn't end up owning anything.  Here it is for your amusement at his retarded butthurt antics.   '''CLICK [[Lionsgate Troll of 2006/transcript|HERE]] FOR THE FULL TRANSCRIPT WITH COMMENTARY, IF YOU WANT IT WITHOUT COMMENTARY, CLICK THE SCREENCAPS ON THIS PAGE, THEY HAVE MOST BUT NOT ALL OF IT'''
