==Analysis==
Hrodulf, believing himself a genius, is in fact a [[moron]].  Having nothing better to do with his life than play [[imaginary|fantasy mind games on the internet]], he deliberately set out to, and succeeded in for a few hours, partially disrupting an [[forum|internet discussion forum]] for a motion picture released by a major distributor, solely because, like a little child who has disturbed an anthill, he was an immature attention whore who wanted to feel powerful by being a dick.  Little did he know that instead of getting angry, the people he trolled instead considered him to be [[crazy|insane]], and the company he thought he "[[own|pwned]]" to this day does not even know about this incident, aside from the moderator who had to clean up after this psychopath's mess.  Great "pwnage" Hrodulf.  Better luck next time, bitch.

